30006546@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1741@LMC@2019-06-15
30006547@@@@@@Many amenities in Nanyang Technological University (NTU) are always fully occupied during certain timings and it’s always hard to find seats in these areas.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1742@LMC@2019-06-15
30006548@@@@@@These amenities include libraries and eating establishments.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1743@LMC@2019-06-15
30006549@@@@@@According to a newsletter by Campus IT team of NTU, it’s always crowded at eating establishments during mealtimes.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1744@LMC@2019-06-15
30006550@@@@@@(NTU, 2013) Thus, there is a need to match resources like seating areas more efficiently to our campus population.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1745@LMC@2019-06-15
30006551@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1746@LMC@2019-06-15
30006552@@@@@@To solve the problem of overcrowding at food establishments, NTU has implemented a ‘CrowdWatch’ system which allows users to view the crowds at food establishments before going over.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1747@LMC@2019-06-15
30006553@@@@@@However, this solution has some limitations.@@@@1@6@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1748@LMC@2019-06-15
30006554@@@@@@Firstly, it’s likely that most of these establishments are equally crowded during lunchtimes, thus, it’s still troublesome to find seats in these areas.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1749@LMC@2019-06-15
30006555@@@@@@Secondly, ‘CrowdWatch’ only targets the eating areas, but not study areas.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1750@LMC@2019-06-15
30006556@@@@@@Students who want to study may find it hard to find seats in the library.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1751@LMC@2019-06-15
