30006564@@@@@@For example, users can check the seat availability in the library before proceeding there, and if they find that the library has few or no available seats, they can proceed to another area with more seats by checking the app.@@@@1@40@ntucle-docid:226; ntucle-sid:1759@LMC@2019-06-15
