30006603@@@@@@The imaging optics will monitor the number of people entering and exiting the study area.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:227; ntucle-sid:1814@LMC@2019-06-15
30006604@@@@@@Installing the sensor only at the entrance/exit provides accuracy in deriving the number of people within the study area.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:227; ntucle-sid:1815@LMC@2019-06-15
30006605@@@@@@The signal processor helps compute the remaining seats available within the study area.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:227; ntucle-sid:1816@LMC@2019-06-15
30006606@@@@@@This figure will then be transmitted with the wireless networking interface via Wireless Local Area Network (WLAN) and uploaded online.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:227; ntucle-sid:1817@LMC@2019-06-15
30006607@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:227; ntucle-sid:1818@LMC@2019-06-15
