30006622@@@@@@Title: Height and Inclination Adjustable Table@@@@1@6@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1645@LMC@2019-06-15
30006623@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1650@LMC@2019-06-15
30006624@@@@@@Many four-legged tables have the problem of being wobbly, often caused by an uneven floor or uneven lengths in the legs of the table.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1651@LMC@2019-06-15
30006625@@@@@@Many products have been developed for this purpose such as table levelers, wedges.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1652@LMC@2019-06-15
30006626@@@@@@Also, with the rise in importance of ergonomics, the need for related tools grow too.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1653@LMC@2019-06-15
30006627@@@@@@This is because ergonomics implements knowledge of body structure and mental issues into creating tools and processes for the people’s usage.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1654@LMC@2019-06-15
30006628@@@@@@-1@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1655@LMC@2019-06-15
30006629@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1656@LMC@2019-06-15
30006630@@@@@@Wobbly tables are a problem to many people as they create annoyance and disturbance to people while they carry out tasks.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1657@LMC@2019-06-15
30006631@@@@@@For example: the wobbling table can cause food and drinks to be spilled out of their containers, writing can become messy.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1658@LMC@2019-06-15
30006632@@@@@@Also, the unsuitable height of tables for people can cause them to end up with bad posture.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1659@LMC@2019-06-15
30006633@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1660@LMC@2019-06-15
30006634@@@@@@The proposed solution is to design a table in which the table will be upright no matter how you place it.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1661@LMC@2019-06-15
30006635@@@@@@The user may also adjust the inclination to his or her needs.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1662@LMC@2019-06-15
30006636@@@@@@The user may also adjust the height of the table for it to be ergonomically suitable for the user.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1663@LMC@2019-06-15
30006637@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1664@LMC@2019-06-15
30006638@@@@@@The design minimizes the disruptions one faces in a wobbly table.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1665@LMC@2019-06-15
30006639@@@@@@It also suits the ergonomic requirements of different individuals by being adjustable.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1666@LMC@2019-06-15
30006640@@@@@@Ergonomics increase efficiency and reduces charges as people are able to work safely and less anxiously without having to sustain work harzards(2).@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1667@LMC@2019-06-15
30006641@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1668@LMC@2019-06-15
30006642@@@@@@The table envisioned is to be made using either aluminum or plastic for light weight.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1669@LMC@2019-06-15
30006643@@@@@@The legs of the table are telescopic legs (3), which is two cylinders within each other for the table leg to be able to have variations in length.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1670@LMC@2019-06-15
30006644@@@@@@At the bottom of the leg, a leveler with a strong spring in it is fitted which ensures that the leg stays in the right place no matter the inclination.@@@@1@30@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1671@LMC@2019-06-15
30006645@@@@@@A rod that extends from the top of the leg to the bottom to secure everything in place.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:229; ntucle-sid:1672@LMC@2019-06-15
