30006761@@@@@@Anti-Haze device@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1857@LMC@2019-06-15
30006762@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1858@LMC@2019-06-15
30006763@@@@@@In 2015, the haze is particularly severe.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1859@LMC@2019-06-15
30006764@@@@@@It is caused by firms and farmers in Indonesia who engage in illegal slash-and-burn practices as they are efficient and inexpensive ways to clear land.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1860@LMC@2019-06-15
30006765@@@@@@The haze has caused several countries in Southeast Asia to be affected and threatens the health of the people.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1861@LMC@2019-06-15
30006766@@@@@@In Indonesia, 10, 000 - 25, 5241 Indonesians have been affected by respiratory illnesses caused by the haze and thousands were forced to flee2.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1862@LMC@2019-06-15
30006767@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1863@LMC@2019-06-15
30006768@@@@@@With haze, other problems and implications have emerged.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1864@LMC@2019-06-15
30006769@@@@@@In Singapore, when Pollution Standards Index (PSI) reaches above the unhealthy range, safety measures will be adopted such as to call off all outdoor activities, especially field games.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1865@LMC@2019-06-15
30006770@@@@@@In many occasions, tournaments have to be cancelled and trainings and events were postponed due to the haze.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1866@LMC@2019-06-15
30006771@@@@@@Some people who loathe sports will not be deterred by the haze but there are no alternatives when it comes to field games.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1867@LMC@2019-06-15
30006772@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1868@LMC@2019-06-15
30006773@@@@@@Therefore, my solution is to have an Anti-Haze device.@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1869@LMC@2019-06-15
30006774@@@@@@This electrical device is made up of several vertical poles planted with a certain distance apart, surrounding the whole field.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1870@LMC@2019-06-15
30006775@@@@@@Each pole is designed with three vertical strips of air column and a flat structure on top of the pole, blowing air horizontally, as shown in the diagram attached.@@@@1@29@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1871@LMC@2019-06-15
30006776@@@@@@When the device is switched on, the vertical air strip facing the field will suck in air to remove the contaminated air, while the other two vertical air strips on the left and right sides of the pole will blow strong wind, creating an air curtain between the poles surrounding the parameters of the field.@@@@1@55@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1872@LMC@2019-06-15
30006777@@@@@@Meanwhile, the flat structures on top of the poles will also blow wind horizontally, creating a horizontal air curtain over the field.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1873@LMC@2019-06-15
30006778@@@@@@These poles will eventually be purifying the air within the enclosed field to allow people to enjoy their sports even when there is haze.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1874@LMC@2019-06-15
