30006782@@@@@@Furthermore, people who enjoyed sports would have less worries for their health when doing sports in the haze.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1878@LMC@2019-06-15
30006783@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:238; ntucle-sid:1879@LMC@2019-06-15
