30007245@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1954@LMC@2019-06-15
30007246@@@@@@In the 21st century, it’s is notable that people and society have become more open about sexuality.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1955@LMC@2019-06-15
