30007261@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1970@LMC@2019-06-15
30007262@@@@@@The most obvious solution would be to change the locks of these doors.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1971@LMC@2019-06-15
30007263@@@@@@The locks need to fulfil its purpose of securing the privacy of the person behind the locks.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1972@LMC@2019-06-15
30007264@@@@@@However, as these locks are used for public toilets for a reason, which is to allow the authorities to have access to whoever is behind the locks should the situation calls for it.@@@@1@33@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1973@LMC@2019-06-15
30007265@@@@@@Hence, the new locks should still have this feature but it is exclusive to the relevant authorities only.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1974@LMC@2019-06-15
30007266@@@@@@The new locks will be designed in such a way that it only opens from the outside with the use of a special key.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1975@LMC@2019-06-15
30007267@@@@@@The key will be modelled after abloy keys, as abloy is a leading company in the market of keys and locks.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1976@LMC@2019-06-15
30007268@@@@@@This enhances the security feature.@@@@1@5@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1977@LMC@2019-06-15
30007269@@@@@@This key will only be held by the relevant authorities which solves the problem of such locks being exploited by potential sexual offenders, and it also gives the user a peace of mind.@@@@1@33@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1978@LMC@2019-06-15
30007270@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1979@LMC@2019-06-15
30007271@@@@@@With this new lock, the locks will fulfil its true purpose as well as deters potential offenders.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1980@LMC@2019-06-15
30007272@@@@@@Indirect benefits such as a possible fall in sexual crimes, could also be reaped from the implementation of the new locks.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1981@LMC@2019-06-15
30007273@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1982@LMC@2019-06-15
30007274@@@@@@This could be done by just identifying the toilets which requires a change in locks.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1983@LMC@2019-06-15
30007275@@@@@@The change in locks is an easy process which does not require much time/effort.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:254; ntucle-sid:1984@LMC@2019-06-15
