30007292@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1945@LMC@2019-06-15
30007293@@@@@@Paper is a daily necessity to many all over the world whether they are at home, in school, in the workplace, or simply partaking of leisurely activities.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1946@LMC@2019-06-15
30007294@@@@@@On average, the annual worldwide usage of paper per person is 48 kilograms (Paper Waste, 2014).@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1947@LMC@2019-06-15
30007295@@@@@@Such high usage of paper means that wastage of paper is rampant.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1948@LMC@2019-06-15
30007296@@@@@@A largely prominent form of paper wastage is through the printing of receipts.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1949@LMC@2019-06-15
30007297@@@@@@Supermarkets, retail stores and food outlets are some of the biggest culprits of this activity.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1950@LMC@2019-06-15
30007298@@@@@@Receipts, which are so commonplace in our daily lives account for 640 000 tons of paper usage and this is why it is an issue I would like to address in this project.@@@@1@33@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1951@LMC@2019-06-15
30007299@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1952@LMC@2019-06-15
30007300@@@@@@Many people have no actual usage for receipts, which are often conveniently tossed aside.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1953@LMC@2019-06-15
30007301@@@@@@The need for tangible paper receipts has slowly diminished with the advancement of technology.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1954@LMC@2019-06-15
30007302@@@@@@Receipts also contribute to the increasing amount of paper wastage.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1955@LMC@2019-06-15
30007303@@@@@@The process of making receipts is disturbingly damaging to the environment.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1956@LMC@2019-06-15
30007304@@@@@@For every 640,000 tons of receipts produced, 249,600,000 gallons of oil are consumed, and extremely high levels of carbon dioxide are emitted which damage our Earth’s ozone layer significantly (Fornes, 2010).@@@@1@31@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1957@LMC@2019-06-15
30007305@@@@@@Therefore, there is a need to eradicate the use of receipts and replace them with electronic receipts.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1958@LMC@2019-06-15
30007306@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1959@LMC@2019-06-15
