30007312@@@@@@The application will correctly display the amount and it will be added to the shopping cart in the application.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1965@LMC@2019-06-15
30007313@@@@@@2@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1966@LMC@2019-06-15
