30007315@@@@@@Upon scanning their items and checking out, users can opt to pay via the application through their credit and debit cards.@@@@1@21@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1968@LMC@2019-06-15
30007316@@@@@@3@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1969@LMC@2019-06-15
30007317@@@@@@Record of Purchases:@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1970@LMC@2019-06-15
30007318@@@@@@The application will then keep a record of the user’s purchases.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1971@LMC@2019-06-15
30007319@@@@@@Receipts will be kept for 6 months, or it can also be manually managed according to the user’s preference.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1972@LMC@2019-06-15
30007320@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:255; ntucle-sid:1973@LMC@2019-06-15
